
Смена фона
3. Повторите страницу по данному по образцу:

<style>
.block {
border: 1px solid red;
height: 200px;
width: 200px;
}
@keyframes anim {
from {background: white;}
to {background: red;}
}
.block {
animation-name: anim;
animation-duration: 3s;
animation-timing-function: ease;
animation-iteration-count: 1;
}
</style>
